# IntelliJ HTTP Client examples for technical-interview-demo
# Operator surface requires ADMIN and an authenticated session.
# Auth errors use the localized ProblemDetail shape with title/status/detail/messageKey/message/language.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@sessionCookie = paste-technical-interview-demo-session-here

### OperatorSurfaceController - get operator inspection surface (ADMIN + authenticated session)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/operator-surface
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Accept: application/json

### OperatorSurfaceController - get operator inspection surface without authentication (401 localized ProblemDetail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/operator-surface
Accept: application/problem+json

### OperatorSurfaceController - get operator inspection surface as non-admin user (403 localized ProblemDetail)
# Replace the session cookie with a regular authenticated USER session.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/operator-surface
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Accept: application/problem+json
